app_name: Groups Control Groups Voice Recording and Karaoke Apps Hear Boost Live Transcribe
app_description: Hearing boost app provides you the way to transcribe speech to text to help deaf people to know what other people say. You have to choose from one of the 40 languages and just start listening. There s also a possibility to enlarge the font for people with poor eyesight. About Subscription The app contains monthly subscription at price 4.99 month. Yearly subscription at price 19.99.
